<section id="overview" class="doc-section">
  <div class="intro-grid">
    <div class="copy-card">
      <p class="korean-line">특정 파일 혹은 폴더를 GitHub에 커밋하고 싶지 않을 때는 <code>.gitignore</code> 파일을 생성하면 됩니다.</p>
      <p class="korean-line">다음과 같이 <code>heavy</code>라는 폴더 안에 있는 모든 자료를 커밋하고 싶지 않다고 합시다.</p>
      <p>You can create a <code>.gitignore</code> file to exclude specific files or folders from your GitHub commits.</p>
      <div class="code-box">
        <pre><code>heavy/</code></pre>
        <p class="small-note">Typical entry for the example shown on the source page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <figure class="image-frame">
      <img src="/assets/images/gitignore/example-folder.png" alt="Example project tree showing the heavy folder">
      <figcaption>Example project state before adding <code>.gitignore</code>.</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-1" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 1</p>
      <p class="korean-line"><code>.gitignore</code>을 최상위 폴더에 생성하세요.</p>
      <p>Create a <code>.gitignore</code> file in the root folder.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="image-frame">
      <img src="/assets/images/gitignore/step1-root-file.png" alt="A new .gitignore file in the project root">
      <figcaption>The file should sit in the project root.</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-2" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 2</p>
      <p class="korean-line">해당 폴더의 이름을 입력하고 저장하세요. 그러면 해당 폴더에 회색 음영이 칠해지는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
      <p>Type the folder name and save it. You will then see that the folder is grayed out.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="figure-stack">
      <figure class="image-frame">
        <img src="/assets/images/gitignore/step2-ignore-entry.png" alt="A .gitignore file containing heavy">
        <figcaption>Add the folder name to <code>.gitignore</code> and save it.</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="image-frame">
        <img src="/assets/images/gitignore/step2-gray-folder.png" alt="VS Code showing the ignored folder grayed out">
        <figcaption>The ignored folder becomes visually dimmed in the explorer.</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="step-3" class="doc-section">
  <div class="doc-section-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="step-label">Step 3</p>
      <p class="korean-line">커밋을 해보면 GitHub에 올라가지 않은 것을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
      <p>If you try committing, you will see that it has not been uploaded to GitHub.</p>
    </div>
    <figure class="image-frame">
