    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="tip" class="callout-card">
  <p class="eyebrow">Tip</p>
  <h2>Why does it not work?</h2>
  <p class="korean-line"><code>.gitignore</code>는 Git에 한 번도 올라가지 않은 파일에만 적용됩니다. 이미 <code>add</code>나 <code>commit</code>한 적이 있다면 무시되지 않습니다.</p>
  <p><code>.gitignore</code> works only on untracked files. It ignores neither staged nor committed files. You need to remove already tracked files from the cache.</p>
  <div class="code-box">
    <pre><code>git rm -r --cached heavy</code></pre>
    <p class="small-note">Example command for a folder that was already tracked earlier.</p>
  </div>
  <p class="source-note">Source page: <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/a-30-year-journey/section-2-usage/2-2-vs-code-github/2-2-8-gitignore?authuser=0">A 30-Year Journey - 2.2.8 Gitignore</a></p>
</section>
